"title": "6609: adoption, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6609: adoption, nature of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The giving by God of the status and privileges of being his children. God adopts those who believe in him and grants them the benefits of his salvation.</p>\n<h2>A family adopts a child</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:3\">GEN 15:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:5\">GEN 48:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:10\">EXO 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:7\">EST 2:7</a></p>\n<h2>God adopts the nation of Israel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:2\">DEU 14:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:7\">DEU 7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:16\">ISA 63:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:1-Amos3:2\">AMO 3:1–3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:4\">ROM 9:4</a></p>\n<h3>God is Israel's father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:9\">JER 31:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:6\">MAL 1:6</a></p>\n<h3>Israel is God's son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1\">HOS 11:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:1\">DEU 14:1</a></p>\n<h2>God adopts believers as his children</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:12-John1:13\">JHN 1:12–1:13</a></strong></p>\n<h3>God is the Father of believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:18\">2CO 6:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:9\">MAT 6:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:2\">LUK 11:2</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are adopted as an outcome of predestination</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:5\">EPH 1:5</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Believers are adopted as an outcome of redemption</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:5\">GAL 4:5</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Believers are adopted as an outcome of justification</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:24-Gal3:26\">GAL 3:24–3:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:12-John1:13\">JHN 1:12–1:13</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are adopted by grace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:3-Eph1:6\">EPH 1:3–1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:3-Ezek16:6\">EZK 16:3–16:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:16\">ROM 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:11\">EPH 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>The final adoption of believers will occur at the resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:23\">ROM 8:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:13–1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2\">1JN 3:2</a></p>",
